# EmailJS Configuration (Required for styled, branded portfolio emails)
# Instructions:
# 1. Sign up/log in at https://www.emailjs.com
# 2. Add an Email Service (e.g. Gmail) and copy the Service ID.
# 3. Create an Email Template, design its layout, and copy the Template ID.
# 4. Find your Public Key in Account -> API Keys and copy it.
# 5. Create a '.env.local' file in this directory and copy these variables with your values.

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_emailjs_service_id
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_emailjs_template_id
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_emailjs_public_key

# Google Analytics Configuration
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=your_google_analytics_measurement_id

